{"tid":1546083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔洗推]投訴\"藍絲\"社署註冊社工何X勝諸事宜","createTime":"2019-09-06T06:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T06:54:38.000Z","uid":87143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46910040f5b867802ac1e0de6d175f11a0fbaaae","tid":1546083,"uid":87143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:54:04.000Z","msg":"強烈譴責  一名社署註冊社工 何X勝 <br />\n<br />\n何偉X此人中學就讀於仁濟醫院羅陳楚思紀念中學 曾當風紀小頭目 (城大社工系副學士以及學士 學歷有待證實)<br />\n<br />\n1. 在外惡劣言行及操守 經常在外 散佈錯誤之政府資訊 、社署&quot;慣常&quot;做法 及 法律資訊 <br />\n<br />\n而該人並無相等學歷給予建議及提供咨詢 <br />\n<br />\n2. 經常指責、中傷並侮辱 反對該人言行之人士 <br />\n<br />\n3. 從未經確實之媒體中引用各種資訊誤導 甚至包括 投資、保險及 財經資訊等 予周遭市民及朋友 但其人並無考取相關資格即提供建議及意見<br />\n<br />\n該社工 與 回饋社會、為市民謀福祉 之 註冊社工 高潔、良好形象不符 <br />\n<br />\n損壞香港市民對社署註冊社工之期望<br />\n<br />\n嚴正懷疑 該社工 有否遵守 註冊社工應有之操守 <br />\n<br />\n希望 以幫助香港市民目的為宗旨 給予警醒該社工 若不能糾正 該社工 在內在外言行及操守 <br />\n<br />\n不排除將訴諸各方及法律 以正視聽<br />\n<br />\n----------------------<br />\n<br />\n此人言行包括 教唆他人(懷疑對象包括執行社工任務時受助人及老人) 將儲蓄全買某股票退休、多買各種保險人壽等投資意見 <br />\n<br />\n、支持警察及政府嚴正執法<span style=\"color: red;\">並將有份參與遊行示威者全部判刑及受罰</span>、以 前陪審員身分提出不具效用之法律意見<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d0HnJUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd0HnJUF.jpg&h=add47dcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t7AXxN0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft7AXxN0.jpg&h=c3cfea8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DrnbCeG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDrnbCeG.jpg&h=5ef926ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4YP1Ztb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4YP1Ztb.jpg&h=2df3afa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ooj5GGx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOoj5GGx.jpg&h=496863b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07e3a3db45e3cd08abd4b50ad46bddc4e8658129","tid":1546083,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:54:34.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b817c1e522750df09951ef61a916843c925ea9f3","tid":1546083,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:54:38.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=35fad63f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"}]}